#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
#: data/campaigns/The_Hammer_of_Thursagan/scenarios/03_Strange_Allies.cfg:255
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "What matters is that these raiders are defeated now. My thanks to you, "
